Model
 - associations spelled correctly
 - accepts_nested_attributes_for any nested attribute associations
 - validates presence of identifying attributes
 - validates uniqueness of identifying attributes
 - ensures creation of associated objects for forms (fields_for won't display anything unless there is a blank object)
 - includes ModelActivityTracker

Controller
 - authenticates user before all actions
 - grid'd

Views
 - action links are in <div class="actions" />
 - titles are capitalized and not underscored